''Update 11/03/2009''

The low start up frequency problem seems to have cured itself, the oscillator now starts around 10.139 MHz and shortly settles at 10.1400035 MHz.

The oscillator feeds a small PA to provide about 2.8W into a 50ohm load (with PA supply at 12v). The output of the PA is bandpass filtered with a couple of re-tuned 10.7 MHz TOKO IF cans which also limit the power output to 13mW into 50ohm (PA supply at 8v).
